PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of FERNE VIRGINIA MacLENNAN, of River Denys, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Gail Rudderham-Chernin, whose term has expired.
